description:
On this episode of ANN International: Hundreds give their hearts to Jesus through baptism during Impact Botswana.

Evangelistic efforts take place across more than 30 countries in Europe during “Christ for Europe”.

Also, Elder Ted Wilson, president of the Adventist Church, visits government authorities in Nigeria and advocates for freedom of conscience for all. 

Stay tuned as ANN brings you these captivating stories and provides coverage of other global news. For a deeper dive into these headlines and beyond, visit adventist.news.
